"有料就係囉<br />\n我呢D趁個市好呃下飯食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"以前做開邊類it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9888c83d7817499cb653c1bd4a87a0da99df6b","tid":1950991,"uid":326897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67af3888b28b473e2dbfe612079587d4622f231f","tid":1950991,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"自殺又唔敢<br />\n中武漢肺炎算啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"點解唔去拎綜援?<br />\n有公屋有雙糧，免費醫療，<br />\n買眼鏡有津貼...<br />\n失業就係人生大贏家嘅開始，<br />\n<br />\n失業...又有咩可怕喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10d7e3e7315d3b6ad71ab34344b54e609ae2c99","tid":1950991,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"師兄做開飲食相關IT?"},{"pid":"557ca50ad6484db6552ac46b831b054b83f5f950","tid":1950991,"uid":27210,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"ff96296c4efa4c9fed3bf91ddc484628bd5503de","tid":1950991,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32ef99a3bcba86b9ef29a798193e6471ba711f6","tid":1950991,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8c19bae45a3e4c0c46c955d2d4ff95439cf9aaa","tid":1950991,"uid":121063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96111e877947732e01b597a49587e28f88593154","tid":1950991,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"有料就係囉<br />\n我呢D趁個市好呃下飯食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"以前做開邊類it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"細公司係有咁既風險<br />\n利申 無野做照出糧"},{"pid":"0bc8fd084b4c6c398c3ecba931361c8187767cc2","tid":1950991,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67af3888b28b473e2dbfe612079587d4622f231f","tid":1950991,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"自殺又唔敢<br />\n中武漢肺炎算啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站             <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2ezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9fd117c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"4458f1c1960b2489110bbb125f21da09a03efbe0","tid":1950991,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"邊度可以中到肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n想中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d358f931115a5607ce935de67bef7fd7ce1ddd","tid":1950991,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"開個group互助啦"},{"pid":"712d7d886e77988cf1c9e7a3ae612f8c87dff739","tid":1950991,"uid":94291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"